### ============================================
### Repository Service

@baseUrl = http://localhost:3004/api/v1/repo
@accessToken = <PASTE_YOUR_ACCESS_TOKEN>
@organizationId = <PASTE_YOUR_ORGANIZATION_ID>

### ============================================
### Health Check
### Expected: 200 OK
### ============================================

GET {{baseUrl}}/health HTTP/1.1

### ============================================
### Create Repository - Success
### Expected: 201 Created
### ============================================

POST {{baseUrl}}/repositories HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

{
  "organizationId": "{{organizationId}}",
  "name": "engineering-intelligence-platform",
  "owner": "RohanGhosh",
  "githubUrl": "https://github.com/RohanGhosh/engineering-intelligence-platform",
  "description": "Production-grade backend platform with AI capabilities."
}

### ============================================
### Create Repository - Duplicate Repository
### Expected: 500 (Will become 409 later)
### ============================================

POST {{baseUrl}}/repositories HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

{
  "organizationId": "{{organizationId}}",
  "name": "engineering-intelligence-platform",
  "owner": "RohanGhosh",
  "githubUrl": "https://github.com/RohanGhosh/engineering-intelligence-platform",
  "description": "Duplicate repository."
}

